    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six, utilizing VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve and 320hp. The longitudinal power plant is mated to a crisp 6-speed G96 manual transaxle, ensuring direct mechanical engagement. It has been meticulously maintained with an IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced clutch assembly. The chassis dynamics are preserved through a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the communicative steering and rear-biased weight distribution intrinsic to the platform. Braking performance is handled by four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, providing excellent thermal dissipation and pedal feel. A mechanically sound example ready for spirited driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
