    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained sedan that perfectly balances luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, with only minor road peppering on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014evidence of honest use rather than neglect. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no tears or heavy bolsters wear, and the dashboard remains crack-free and vibrant. All electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the updated infotainment system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust. It has undergone regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the transmission shifts smoothly without hesitation. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brake pads were replaced just last season. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle with a clean title in hand. It represents a dependable, attractive option for anyone seeking a high-quality daily driver without the new-car price tag.",
